## ğŸ› ï¸ Tech Stack

- **Frontend**: HTML, JavaScript
- **Backend**: AWS Lambda (Node.js 20.x)
- **Image Processing**: Sharp (Lambda Layer)
- **API**: Amazon API Gateway (REST)
- **Storage**: Amazon S3
- **Security**: Presigned URLs
- **Hosting**: S3 Static Website Hosting


